            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, spread your <strong>mayo</strong> on the <strong>warmed brioche base</strong>, then top with the <strong>quick-pickled cucumber discs </strong>and <strong>crispy fried chicken</strong>, then drizzle the <strong>chilli oil </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) over the top</p><p>Top with the <strong>warmed brioche bun lid</strong> and serve the<strong> fries </strong>and <strong>quick-pickled cucumber batons </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
